    "This finding emphasizes that social media meaning-making occurs not through one-sided messaging, but through conversations, with each kind of interaction offering a unique contribution to the broader discourse.",
    "This analysis of tweet types begins to explore the relationship between framing and the affordances of social media platforms.",
    "Future research can unpack this relationship more: how do platform affordances affect collective action framing?",
    "Do differences in affordances across platforms shape how social movement mobilization strategies?",
